   "text": "I made a folder for feminism."
  },
  {
   "start": 453.85,
   "end": 455.15,
   "text": "And then I made a folder for, uh."
  },
  {
   "start": 455.61,
   "end": 455.89,
   "text": "Philosophy."
  },
  {
   "start": 456.11,
   "end": 456.93,
   "text": "And then for religion."
  },
  {
   "start": 458.13,
   "end": 458.91,
   "text": "But then I was like."
  },
  {
   "start": 458.93,
   "end": 459.23,
   "text": "You know what?"
  },
  {
   "start": 459.25,
   "end": 460.05,
   "text": "This isn't what I want to do."
  },
  {
   "start": 460.05,
   "end": 461.37,
   "text": "I want to have it all."
  },
  {
   "start": 462.09,
   "end": 462.29,
   "text": "You know."
  },
  {
   "start": 462.39,
   "end": 463.57,
   "text": "The philosophy and religion."
  },
  {
   "start": 463.73,
   "end": 463.85,
   "text": "All that."
  },
  {
   "start": 463.95,
   "end": 464.21,
   "text": "And feminism."
  },
  {
   "start": 464.39,
   "end": 465.61,
   "text": "All in their own countries."
  },
  {
   "start": 466.41,
   "end": 467.19,
   "text": "It needs to be organized."
  },
  {
   "start": 467.43,
   "end": 468.01,
   "text": "Not by subject."
  },
  {
   "start": 468.21,
   "end": 468.67,
   "text": "Or by countries."
  },
  {
   "start": 468.73,
   "end": 469.23,
   "text": "And I also had a."
  },
  {
   "start": 469.33,
   "end": 470.11,
   "text": "I had one for like."
  },
  {
   "start": 470.97,
   "end": 471.45,
   "text": "Enlightenment."
  },
  {
   "start": 472.53,
   "end": 472.93,
   "text": "Uh."
  },
  {
   "start": 472.95,
   "end": 473.95,
   "text": "Industrial revolution."
  },
  {
   "start": 474.13,
   "end": 475.15,
   "text": "Scientific revolution."
  },
  {
   "start": 476.07,
   "end": 476.43,
   "text": "You know."
  },
  {
   "start": 476.45,
   "end": 477.71,
   "text": "And everything enlightenment related."
  },
  {
   "start": 477.91,
   "end": 478.99,
   "text": "And it's own thing."
  },
  {
   "start": 479.05,
   "end": 479.27,
   "text": "You know."
  },
  {
   "start": 479.31,
   "end": 480.33,
   "text": "And then like the dark age."
  },
  {
   "start": 480.37,
   "end": 480.83,
   "text": "And the middle ages."
  },
  {
   "start": 480.95,
   "end": 482.35,
   "text": "And I need to break that up."
  },
  {
   "start": 482.37,
   "end": 483.39,
   "text": "And put them into their own countries."
  },
  {
   "start": 483.49,
   "end": 484.75,
   "text": "So I did waste a lot of time that way."
  },
  {
   "start": 484.81,
   "end": 486.65,
   "text": "But at least I'm glad that I have it figured out now."
  },
  {
   "start": 487.11,
   "end": 490.43,
   "text": "And I'm excited what the final thing is going to look like."
  },
  {
   "start": 490.43,
   "end": 491.85,
   "text": "Because it's really going to give some identity."
  },
  {
   "start": 492.47,
   "end": 494.47,
   "text": "Separate identity to the different countries."
  },
  {
   "start": 494.91,
   "end": 494.93,
   "text": "Um."
  },
  {
   "start": 495.89,
   "end": 496.43,
   "text": "So yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 496.55,
   "end": 497.27,
   "text": "I've got like."
  },
  {
   "start": 497.33,
   "end": 497.61,
   "text": "Uh."
  },
  {
   "start": 498.33,
   "end": 500.39,
   "text": "270 different folders."
  },
  {
   "start": 500.81,
   "end": 501.67,
   "text": "In religion."
  },
  {
   "start": 501.67,
   "end": 502.93,
   "text": "That I have to."
  },
  {
   "start": 503.13,
   "end": 503.43,
   "text": "Um."
  },
  {
   "start": 503.69,
   "end": 505.87,
   "text": "Well I have to find out where the authors are from."
  },
  {
   "start": 506.71,
   "end": 508.03,
   "text": "And then put them in their countries."
  },
  {
   "start": 508.15,
   "end": 509.73,
   "text": "And even attach dates to a lot of them."
  },
  {
   "start": 509.79,
   "end": 510.81,
   "text": "But that's not totally important."
  },
  {
   "start": 510.93,
   "end": 511.93,
   "text": "Just putting them in the right country."
  },
  {
   "start": 512.01,
   "end": 512.35,
   "text": "In the right."
  },
  {
   "start": 512.73,
   "end": 513.69,
   "text": "Period within that country."
  },
  {
   "start": 513.77,
   "end": 514.09,
   "text": "If I want."
  },
  {
   "start": 514.85,
   "end": 515.39,
   "text": "And uh."
  },
  {
   "start": 515.39,
   "end": 515.57,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 515.77,
   "end": 516.91,
   "text": "And then when I get that ready."
  },
  {
   "start": 517.01,
   "end": 517.53,
   "text": "I'll show it."
  },
  {
   "start": 517.61,
   "end": 517.97,
   "text": "But uh."
  },
  {
   "start": 517.97,
   "end": 518.13,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 518.13,
   "end": 519.11,
   "text": "I'm excited about that."
  },
  {
   "start": 519.63,
   "end": 519.91,
   "text": "Um."
  },
  {
   "start": 522.37,
   "end": 522.69,
   "text": "Um."
  },
  {
   "start": 522.69,
   "end": 523.61,
   "text": "I'm parked here."
  },
  {
   "start": 523.61,
   "end": 524.01,
   "text": "Um."
  },
  {
   "start": 524.61,
   "end": 526.75,
   "text": "At the place where I told the cops I would be parked."
  },
  {
   "start": 526.95,
   "end": 528.33,
   "text": "It's the first time I actually parked in here."
  },
  {
   "start": 528.33,
   "end": 530.25,
   "text": "I was driving down the other."
  },
  {
   "start": 530.35,
   "end": 531.23,
   "text": "The other road last."
  },
  {
   "start": 531.41,
   "end": 531.73,
   "text": "Yesterday."
  },
  {
   "start": 532.09,
   "end": 533.57,
   "text": "And I think I'll park there tomorrow."
  },
  {
   "start": 534.35,
   "end": 535.71,
   "text": "And just keep it spaced out."
  },
  {
   "start": 535.79,
   "end": 537.81,
   "text": "Because somebody laid on the horn on me this morning."
  },
  {
   "start": 537.93,
   "end": 538.09,
   "text": "You know."
  },
  {
   "start": 539.13,
   "end": 540.03,
   "text": "When people do that."
  },
  {
   "start": 540.09,
   "end": 540.35,
   "text": "Before."
  },
  {
   "start": 540.47,
   "end": 541.11,
   "text": "When I was in Tucson."
  },
  {
   "start": 541.25,
   "end": 542.19,
   "text": "I thought they were saying hi."
  },
  {
   "start": 542.27,
   "end": 543.35,
   "text": "But then they called the cops on me."
  },
  {
   "start": 543.39,
   "end": 544.31,
   "text": "So when I do that now."
  },
  {
   "start": 544.35,
   "end": 545.47,
   "text": "I know that they're not saying hi."
  },
  {
   "start": 545.95,
   "end": 546.73,
   "text": "Some of them might."
  },
  {
   "start": 546.73,
   "end": 548.95,
   "text": "But I think a lot of them."
  },
  {
   "start": 549.63,
   "end": 550.73,
   "text": "At least the ones who call the cops."
  },
  {
   "start": 550.81,
   "end": 551.07,
   "text": "Are like."
  },
  {
   "start": 551.81,
   "end": 552.37,
   "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
   "start": 552.45,
   "end": 554.27,
   "text": "What the fuck is going on in their heads dude."
  },
  {
   "start": 554.63,
   "end": 555.15,
   "text": "Anything."
  },
  {
   "start": 556.99,
   "end": 557.75,
   "text": "So um."
  },
  {
   "start": 558.89,
   "end": 559.41,
   "text": "I'm here."
  },
  {
   "start": 560.19,
   "end": 561.55,
   "text": "Cooking up my chow chow."
  },
  {
   "start": 562.37,
   "end": 563.45,
   "text": "And that's going to boil."
  },
  {
   "start": 563.87,
   "end": 564.75,
   "text": "And when it boils."
  },
  {
   "start": 564.89,
   "end": 566.05,
   "text": "I'm going to throw the rice in."
  },
  {
   "start": 566.55,
   "end": 567.99,
   "text": "And then I'll just let it cool."
  },
  {
   "start": 568.09,
   "end": 569.55,
   "text": "I probably should have cooked it up with this one."
  },
  {
   "start": 569.59,
   "end": 570.51,
   "text": "Because this one has the top."
  },
  {
   "start": 570.55,
   "end": 571.31,
   "text": "And it can keep the heat."
  },
  {
   "start": 572.45,
   "end": 572.81,
   "text": "Um."
  },
  {
   "start": 573.13,
   "end": 573.45,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 573.51,
   "end": 574.31,
   "text": "I am going to need hungry."
  },
  {
   "start": 574.47,
   "end": 575.33,
   "text": "Dinner here pretty soon."
  },
  {
   "start": 575.39,
   "end": 576.33,
   "text": "I think I'll have those grapes."
  },
  {
   "start": 576.33,
   "end": 576.97,
   "text": "And these carrots."
  },
  {
   "start": 577.07,
   "end": 577.89,
   "text": "So maybe I'll leave you on dinner."
  },
  {
   "start": 578.83,
   "end": 579.15,
   "text": "Um."
  },
  {
   "start": 580.61,
   "end": 581.87,
   "text": "Because I don't think that's going to be ready."
  },
  {
   "start": 583.03,
   "end": 584.59,
   "text": "I'll probably have that for lunch tomorrow."
  },
  {
   "start": 586.68,
   "end": 587.9,
   "text": "Or maybe I'll just get up later."
  },
  {
   "start": 588.0,
   "end": 588.52,
   "text": "And eat some of that."
  },
  {
   "start": 590.14,
   "end": 591.38,
   "text": "But the rice part won't be ready."
  },
  {
   "start": 591.74,
   "end": 592.68,
   "text": "The veggie part will though."
  },
  {
   "start": 592.88,
   "end": 593.96,
   "text": "So maybe I'll just have that."
  },
  {
   "start": 595.08,
   "end": 595.58,
   "text": "There's some."
  },
  {
   "start": 595.66,
   "end": 596.96,
   "text": "My last can of tuna is in there."
  },
  {
   "start": 597.44,
   "end": 597.68,
   "text": "Um."
  },
  {
   "start": 598.2,
   "end": 598.6,
   "text": "I got it."
  },
  {
   "start": 598.62,
   "end": 598.72,
   "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
   "start": 598.78,
   "end": 600.28,
   "text": "And I also got a fruit drink."
  },
  {
   "start": 600.28,
   "end": 600.66,
   "text": "So yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 600.74,
   "end": 601.56,
   "text": "I guess I spent about."
  },
  {
   "start": 602.98,
   "end": 603.82,
   "text": "Fifteen bucks today."
  },
  {
   "start": 603.94,
   "end": 605.78,
   "text": "Because I got a fruit drink for $4.50 at the gym."
  },
  {
   "start": 606.3,
   "end": 607.54,
   "text": "Which had 20 grams of protein."
  },
  {
   "start": 607.54,
   "end": 608.28,
   "text": "And so then I'll have."
  },
  {
   "start": 608.62,
   "end": 609.82,
   "text": "I'm going to have 10 grams of protein."
  },
  {
   "start": 610.6,
   "end": 612.52,
   "text": "So I have to have like another 20 grams of protein."
  },
  {
   "start": 613.54,
   "end": 613.9,
   "text": "Um."
  },
  {
   "start": 614.54,
   "end": 615.8,
   "text": "Or 30 grams of protein."
  },
  {
   "start": 616.0,
   "end": 617.18,
   "text": "25 grams of protein."
  },
  {
   "start": 617.86,
   "end": 618.88,
   "text": "And my protein powder."
  },
  {
   "start": 619.0,
   "end": 619.72,
   "text": "So I guess one scoop."
  },
  {
   "start": 620.72,
   "end": 621.14,
   "text": "Um."
  },
  {
   "start": 622.34,
   "end": 622.7,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 623.4,
   "end": 624.58,
   "text": "So that's what I did today."
  },
  {
   "start": 626.58,
   "end": 627.78,
   "text": "Peace out doggy style."
  },
  {
   "start": 628.7,
   "end": 629.1,
   "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
   "start": 629.2,
   "end": 629.7,
   "text": "What's up."
  },
  {
   "start": 629.76,
   "end": 630.16,
   "text": "Hey hey."
  },
  {
   "start": 630.32,
   "end": 632.66,
   "text": "I got two donationists today."
  },
  {
   "start": 632.8,
   "end": 635.78,
   "text": "And I wanted to show them what happens when you get a donation."
  },
  {
   "start": 636.0,
   "end": 637.58,
   "text": "When you become a donationist."
  },
  {
   "start": 638.26,
   "end": 640.16,
   "text": "You can push this button right here in my timeline."
  },
  {
   "start": 640.38,
   "end": 642.16,
   "text": "Or a button on my homepage."
  },
  {
   "start": 643.2,
   "end": 644.94,
   "text": "Now I'm doing it this way on Dreamweaver."
  },
  {
   "start": 644.94,
   "end": 648.1,
   "text": "Because I can't fucking figure out how to make these goddamn links work."
  },
  {
   "start": 648.36,
   "end": 649.74,
   "text": "And since I got Dreamweaver 5."
  },
  {
   "start": 649.84,
   "end": 652.08,
   "text": "It's become complete fucking rocket science."
  },
  {
   "start": 653.24,
   "end": 654.84,
   "text": "So we'll figure that out later."
  },
  {
   "start": 654.94,
   "end": 656.08,
   "text": "But I want to donate this video."
  },
  {
   "start": 656.32,
   "end": 656.44,
   "text": "So."
  },
  {
   "start": 657.46,
   "end": 657.86,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 657.98,
   "end": 659.14,
   "text": "First 100 donators."
  },
  {
   "start": 659.28,
   "end": 660.68,
   "text": "And biggest 100 donators."
  },
  {
   "start": 660.8,
   "end": 661.08,
   "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
   "start": 661.08,
   "end": 665.86,
   "text": "Now I've got a couple of people who are on both of my first donators page."
  },
  {
   "start": 666.06,
   "end": 666.66,
   "text": "And my biggest."
  },
  {
   "start": 667.42,
   "end": 668.34,
   "text": "Included my uncle."
  },
  {
   "start": 668.5,
   "end": 669.96,
   "text": "Because he gave me 50 bucks."
  },
  {
   "start": 670.8,
   "end": 671.7,
   "text": "A year ago."
  },
  {
   "start": 671.8,
   "end": 673.18,
   "text": "And that wasn't even for this project."
  },
  {
   "start": 673.36,
   "end": 674.98,
   "text": "But I included him because I was working on the project."
  },
  {
   "start": 675.08,
   "end": 676.7,
   "text": "And my mom yesterday gave me 5 bucks."
  },
  {
   "start": 677.36,
   "end": 677.76,
   "text": "Whoops."
  },
  {
   "start": 678.02,
   "end": 678.7,
   "text": "I don't have to write that."
  },
  {
   "start": 679.64,
   "end": 682.42,
   "text": "And then I got a donation from Andrew Tandoy."
  },
  {
   "start": 682.72,
   "end": 684.48,
   "text": "He's in the Hall of the Immortals."
  },
  {
   "start": 685.28,
   "end": 685.86,
   "text": "For $10."
  },
  {
   "start": 686.46,
   "end": 688.54,
   "text": "And then Melody James from Australia."
  },
  {
   "start": 689.28,
   "end": 690.66,
   "text": "He's in the Hall of the Immortals."
  },
  {
   "start": 690.66,
   "end": 691.22,
   "text": "For $22."
  },
  {
   "start": 691.56,
   "end": 694.26,
   "text": "And not only are they in their first donationist's page."
  },
  {
   "start": 694.9,
   "end": 698.0,
   "text": "But they are in the biggest donationist's page."
  },
  {
   "start": 698.26,
   "end": 700.68,
   "text": "First place is Richard Kyle."
  },
  {
   "start": 701.26,
   "end": 702.42,
   "text": "With the silver medal."
  },
  {
   "start": 702.64,
   "end": 704.7,
   "text": "You have Melody James."
  },
  {
   "start": 705.78,
   "end": 708.04,
   "text": "Alan Andrew Tandoy is in the bronze medal."
  },
  {
   "start": 708.48,
   "end": 709.5,
   "text": "In the Hall of the Immortals."
  },
  {
   "start": 710.1,
   "end": 713.34,
   "text": "And my mother is considered a rich motherfucker."
  },
  {
   "start": 714.0,
   "end": 714.98,
   "text": "And all she gave was $5."
  },
  {
   "start": 716.12,
   "end": 718.84,
   "text": "So I just wanted to show how the system worked."
  },
  {
   "start": 718.84,
   "end": 720.96,
   "text": "And that's enough."
  },
  {
   "start": 720.96,
   "end": 750.94,
   "text": "Thank you."
